flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> A[User enters natural<br/>language query]
    A --> B{Input validation<br/>passes?}
    B -->|No| C[Display error message<br/>with guidance]
    C --> A
    B -->|Yes| E[Convert query to<br/>vector embedding]
    E --> F1[Keyword Search<br/>ParadeDB BM25]
    E --> F2[Semantic Search<br/>pgvector Cosine Similarity]
    E --> F3[Title Similarity<br/>pgvector on Title Embeddings]
    F1 --> G[Merge results using<br/>Reciprocal Rank Fusion<br/>title_boost = 1.5x]
    F2 --> G
    F3 --> G
    G --> G2[Rerank top results<br/>via Cohere Rerank v3.5]
    G2 --> G25[Apply RBAC filter<br/>by user role and access level]
    G25 --> G3[Apply version filter<br/>show latest only]
    G3 --> I{Results<br/>found?}
    I -->|No| J["Display 'No results found'<br/>with suggestions and tips"]
    J --> K{User refines<br/>query?}
    K -->|Yes| A
    K -->|No| End1([End])
    I -->|Yes| L[Display ranked results:<br/>title, snippet, author,<br/>date, type]
    L --> P{User applies<br/>filters?}
    P -->|Yes| A
    P -->|No| Q{User refines<br/>query?}
    Q -->|Yes| A
    Q -->|No| End3([End])
